hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: When can you start? bupropion sr 300 mg side effects I’m living testament that all aging fans are not well heeled and I’m certainly not willing or able to pay high ticket prices. The last 2 concerts I attended were Dr.John in Karlsruhe Germany and Dr. John and Van Morrison at a Lorelei Rock mountain concert, in the late 90′s.. Both were far less than $100 and both provided a lifetime of good memories. Wilco also appeared at the same Lorelei venue. My only regret is I’ve never been to a live John Prine concert. I guess I’ll have to content myself with listening to LP’s and Cd’s and continue to enjoy the music that accompanied me throughout my journey in life. What could be better than hunker down with my favorite beer listening to the John Prine and Mac Wiseman album, Standard Songs For Average People album. The title says it all. Priceless.
